OL,3,CPlans for joined up health care
OL,4,Camounted to 'a lot of meetings'
OL,6,FThe history of collaboration between
OL,7,FGuernsey and Jersey isn't a good one.
OL,9,FFrom the ferry debacle that continues
OL,10,Fto rumble on, to an infamous falling
OL,11,Fout over inter-island electricity that
OL,12,Fled to a Guernsey Deputy reading the
OL,13,Friot act... this has rarely been a
OL,14,Fjoined-up archipelago.
OL,16,FAnd now questions are being asked
OL,17,Fabout big promises to join up health
OL,18,Fcare.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
