FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780873386
OL,3,CPlans for joined up health care
OL,4,Camounted to 'a lot of meetings'
OL,6,FIn 2024, both governments made a lot
OL,7,Fof noise about a collaborative group,
OL,8,Fofficially named the Channel Island
OL,9,FAlliance for Health and Social Care.
OL,11,FThe guiding principles included taking
OL,12,Fa "whole system approach" to make
OL,13,Fhealth care more resilient across both
OL,14,Fislands, and focussing on
OL,15,Fopportunities for joint working.
OL,17,FThe idea wasn't without merit, but was
OL,18,Fcriticised at the time for essentially
OL,19,Fboiling down to a few meetings.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780873386
OL,3,CPlans for joined up health care
OL,4,Camounted to 'a lot of meetings'
OL,6,FThe idea cooled almost immediately
OL,7,Fafter it was announced, as both
OL,8,Fislands tackled various issues with
OL,9,Ftheir respective hospitals.
OL,11,FIn fact, Jersey's Minister for Health
OL,12,Fand Social Services said it was a good
OL,13,Fidea, but pointless if your own house
OL,14,Fisn't in order.
OL,16,FA Deputy in Guernsey is now probing
OL,17,Fits Health and Social Care department
OL,18,F(HSC) on the Alliance, and what became
OL,19,Fof it, asking a series of questions
OL,20,Fabout what has actually been done.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780873386
OL,3,CPlans for joined up health care
OL,4,Camounted to 'a lot of meetings'
OL,6,FDeputy Tom Rylatt said: "We face the
OL,7,Fchallenge of trying to provide the
OL,8,Fhealth care service of a small
OL,9,Fcountry, while being the size of a
OL,10,Fsmall town.
OL,12,F"If there are opportunities for
OL,13,FGuernsey to work with Jersey in a way
OL,14,Fthat delivers better outcomes for
OL,15,Fpatients and better value for
OL,16,Ftaxpayers, then we should be pursuing
OL,17,Fthem."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780873386
OL,3,CPlans for joined up health care
OL,4,Camounted to 'a lot of meetings'
OL,6,FHe was told that officers on each
OL,7,Fisland work together quite frequently
OL,8,Fand was provided with a list of
OL,9,Fworkstreams where collaboration does
OL,10,Ftake place.
OL,12,FThis included meetings about
OL,13,Fmedicines, meetings about pharmacies,
OL,14,FDirector meetings, screening meetings,
OL,15,Fand NHS meetings.
OL,17,F"I'm not fully satisfied with the
OL,18,Fresponse," Deputy Rylatt explained.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780873386
OL,3,CPlans for joined up health care
OL,4,Camounted to 'a lot of meetings'
OL,6,F"I welcome the level of engagement
OL,7,Fbetween officers in Guernsey and
OL,8,FJersey and there are some positive
OL,9,Fexamples of collaboration.
OL,11,F"However, the response describes a lot
OL,12,Fof meetings and information-sharing
OL,13,Fbut provides less evidence of tangible
OL,14,Foutcomes."
OL,16,FHe also asked whether a formal body
OL,17,Fcould ever be set up, something he
OL,18,Fcalls a Joint Health Authority, which
OL,19,Fmay be more impactful in shaping
OL,20,Fpolicy or sharing resources and
OL,21,Ffacilities.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780873386
OL,3,CPlans for joined up health care
OL,4,Camounted to 'a lot of meetings'
OL,6,FIn response, the President of HSC,
OL,7,FDeputy George Oswald, said: "The
OL,8,Fsubject of a Joint Health Authority
OL,9,Fwas discussed at this meeting but was
OL,10,Fnot supported politically in either
OL,11,FBailiwick at that time."
OL,13,FWith a new government on the horizon
OL,14,Fin Jersey and the ink still wet on a
OL,15,Fdeal for its long-awaited hospital at
OL,16,FOverdale, perhaps there will be fresh
OL,17,Fpolitical appetite for closer ties
OL,18,Fgoing forward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
